Package: IndiaTS
Type: Package
Title: Common Time Series Utilities for Indian Economic and Financial Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Indranil", "Gayen",
      email = "nil.gayen@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    ))
Description: 
    Provides a consistent and tidy framework for common time series
    manipulations frequently used in Indian macroeconomic and fiscal
    analysis. The package supports transformations such as month-on-month,
    quarter-on-quarter, and year-on-year growth rates, CAGR and SAAR
    calculations, seasonal adjustment, and calendar-based conversions.
    Core functionality is built around an intermediate 'time-dataframe'
    (tdf) abstraction that enables seamless integration with the tidyverse
    ecosystem, including 'dplyr', 'ggplot2', and related tools, while
    remaining compatible with base R time series objects.
